    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level is considered medium due to the function's role in validating table references, which involve multiple checks or conditions. The complexity can increase if the function includes intricate logic to handle various scenarios or edge cases related to table references."
